cards.text:
_Warp 2_ -- {f}{1}
When Ramza enters the field, choose 1 _Job Knight_ of cost 5 or less in your Break Zone. Play it onto the field.
Dull 4 active _Job Knight_: Choose 1 Forward opponent controls. Break it. Ramza deals your opponent 1 point of damage.

_Warp 2_ -- {i}{i}
If your opponent has 2 cards or less in their hand, Teodor gains +2000 power, **Haste** and **First Strike**.
When Teodor enters the field due to Warp, your opponent discards 1 card.

_Warp 3_ -- {e}{1}
If Yumcax is dealt damage, reduce the damage by 2000 instead.
_Damage 3_ -- Yumcax gains **Brave** and "When Yumcax is put from the field into the Break Zone, draw 1 card."

_Warp 2_ -- {u}
When Rinoa enters the field, you may pay {x}. When you do so, choose 1 Forward of cost X or less. Put it into the Break Zone.
[Angelo Cannon] {S}, reveal 1 Forward in your hand: Choose 1 Forward. Deal it damage equal to the power of the Forward you revealed.

_Warp 4_ - {u}{u}
When Lunafreya enters the field, draw 2 cards.
When Lunafreya enters the field due to Warp, draw 1 card.

_Warp 1_ -- {i}{w}
When Melvien enters the field, choose up to 2 Backups and up to 2 other Backups. Activate the former and Freeze the latter.
When Melvien is put from the field into the Break Zone, you may remove Melvien from the game. When you do so, place 2 Warp Counters on Melvien.

Warp 3 - {f}{1}
**Brave**
Tifa can attack twice in the same turn.

Warp 4 - {l}{2}
When a Warp Counter is removed from Golbez, you may play 1 _Job Archfiend_ from your hand onto the field. When you do so, draw 1 card. This effect will trigger only if Golbez is removed from the game.
All the _Job Archfiend_ Forwards you control gain +3000 power.

Warp 2 - {i}{e}{2}
When Prishe in your hand is removed from the game due to Warp, choose 1 Forward. Deal it 8000 damage.
When Prishe enters the field, choose up to 1 Forward and up to 1 Backup. Dull them and Freeze them.

Warp 1 - {w}{l}
**Haste** **Brave**
[Hurricane] {S}{w}{l}{1}{D}: Choose 1 Forward. Break it.

Warp 2 - {e}{u}
When Garnet enters the field, choose 1 Summon in your Break Zone. Add it to your hand.
When Garnet enters the field due to Warp, choose 1 Summon in your Break Zone. Add it to your hand.

Warp 2 - {f}{l}
{EX} When Zack enters the field, choose 1 Forward. Deal it 7000 damage.
When Zack enters the field due to Warp, until the end of the turn, Zack gains **Haste**, **First Strike** and **Brave**.

Warp 2 - {f}
**Haste**
{EX} When Morrow enters the field due to Warp, draw 2 cards, then discard 1 card.

Warp 2 - {w}
When a Warp Counter is removed from Bel Dat, your opponent puts the top 2 cards of their deck into the Break Zone. This effect will trigger only if Bel Dat is removed from the game.
When Bel Dat enters the field, choose 1 Forward in your opponent's Break Zone. Remove it from the game. You can cast it as though you owned it at any time you could normally cast it.

Warp 3 - {l}
When Sephiroth enters the field, choose 1 Forward other than Sephiroth. Break it.
[Zanshin] {S}: Choose 1 Forward of cost 3 or less. Break it.

Warp 4 - {0}
When a Warp Counter is removed from Mist, look at the top card of your deck. You may put it into the Break Zone. This effect will trigger only if Mist is removed from the game.
When Mist enters the field, draw 1 card.

Warp 3 - {u}
When Lunafreya enters the field, your opponent selects 1 Forward they control. Put it into the Break Zone.
When Lunafreya enters the field due to Warp, choose 1 Forward opponent controls. Return it to its owner's hand.
